enCodeRAG** delivers a local-first semantic code search pipeline with AST\nchunking, incremental indexing, configurable embeddings, LanceDB vector\nstorage, a CLI, and OpenCode plugin integration.\n\nKey strengths:\n\n- Local + privacy-first\n- Modular architecture (interfaces + factory/adapter patterns)\n- Workspace-native\n- No native build tools required (WASM-based parsing)\n\nKey next steps:\n\n1. Hybrid search + re-ranking — retrieval quality\n2. Code graph integration — structural code understanding\n3. Context window optimization — better result packing for prompts\n```\n\n[/home/christoph/code/OpenCodeRAG/AGENTS.md:118-122] (markdown, score: 0.54)\n```markdown\n### OpenCode plugin types\n`@opencode-ai/plugin` lives in `.opencode/node_modules/` — not installed via\nnpm. Declare types locally in `src/types/opencode-plugin.d.ts` rather than\nadding a dependency.\n```\n\n[/home/christoph/code/OpenCodeRAG/src/types/opencode-plugin.d.ts:6-6] (typescript, score: 0.54)\n```typescript\nexport type { ToolDefinition } from \"@opencode-ai/plugin/tool\";\n```\n\n[/home/christoph/code/OpenCodeRAG/package.json:31-33] (json, score: 0.53)\n```json\n\"bin\": {\n    \"opencode-rag\": \"./dist/cli.js\"\n  }\n```\n\n[/home/christoph/code/OpenCodeRAG/src/plugin.ts:105-122] (typescript, score: 0.53)\n```typescript\nfunction buildToolQuery(tool: string, output: string): string {\n  const normalized = normalizeToolOutput(output);\n  if (!normalized) return \"\";\n\n  const lines = normalized\n    .split(\"\\n\")\n    .map((line) => line.trim())\n    .filter((line) => line.length > 0)\n    .slice(0, 40);\n\n  if (lines.length === 0) return \"\";\n\n  return [\n    `OpenCode used the ${tool} tool while searching for relevant files and code.`,\n    \"Use these discovered paths and matches as retrieval hints:\",\n    ...lines,\n  ].join(\"\\n\");\n}\n```\n\n[/home/christoph/code/OpenCodeRAG/package.json:4-4] (json, score: 0.53)\n```json\n\"description\": \"OpenCode plugin for local-first RAG-based semantic code search\"\n```\n\n---\n"}

